{"tid":983475,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台北市無差別瘋狂殺人案　兇徒被移送途中　台灣群眾義憤等候追打","createTime":"2019-01-16T04:00:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-16T04:02:05.000Z","uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"99134364743b0f56f386e8657cae4e7fa92475a0","tid":983475,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T04:00:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/society/breakingnews/1013610\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fsociety%2Fbreakingnews%2F1013610&d=83FBbTagrh2ptgyisIq3y5UJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=470c48bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fsociety%2Fbreakingnews%2F1013610&h=3bb44be6\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/society/breakingnews/1013610</a><br />\n<br />\n台灣首件捷運瘋狂殺人事件，凶嫌鄭捷今天凌晨0時45分，被警方由板橋江翠派出所移送到板橋海山警分局，在移送過程中，鄭嫌口戴口罩不發一語，由警方大陣仗押送，在步出派出所時，憤怒的民眾激動得衝上前去，混亂之中，鄭捷挨了好幾記憤怒的拳頭，民眾隨後被警方隔離，並將鄭捷推入警車中移送。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.tvbs.com.tw/life/532479\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvbs.com.tw%2Flife%2F532479&d=83FBbTagrh2ptgyisIq3y5UJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=d7494431\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.tvbs.com.tw/life/532479</a><br />\n<br />\n捷運無差別殺人，鄭捷如同奪命閻羅，殺紅雙眼，一整夜的偵訊移送，民眾一路唾罵追打，但鄭捷始終不發一語，神情木然，新北地院上午6點召開聲押庭，隨即裁定鄭捷羈押。<br />\n<br />\n走出派出所，鄭捷眉頭帶著傷，臉頰也有瘀血的痕跡，儘管警方團團將他圍住，還是有人偷襲成功。但不只這一位，鄭捷揮刀殺人，氣憤的大批民眾，早在外頭等著兇手。<br />\n<br />\n一看到鄭捷，激動情緒瞬間引爆。一句句畜生、禽獸，四面八方意圖向兇手招呼的拳頭，警方幾乎擋不住，只能護著兇手的頭，一路壓著往車裡推。移往海山分局，同樣有民眾等在這兒。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cc.tvbs.com.tw/news2.0/img/FILE_DB/newsphoto/shihwei8@tvbs.com.tw/201405/20140522145520477.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcc.tvbs.com.tw%2Fnews2.0%2Fimg%2FFILE_DB%2Fnewsphoto%2Fshihwei8%40tvbs.com.tw%2F201405%2F20140522145520477.JPG&h=008aa403&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cc.tvbs.com.tw/news2.0/img/FILE_DB/newsphoto/okinawa29@tvbs.com.tw/201405/20140522140906598.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcc.tvbs.com.tw%2Fnews2.0%2Fimg%2FFILE_DB%2Fnewsphoto%2Fokinawa29%40tvbs.com.tw%2F201405%2F20140522140906598.jpg&h=b8de3a07&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d9d78c59c98264d29de8c103ba72a32cc4cd95f","tid":983475,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T04:01:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"830c66fb972604c1496c878eade78c4b82ba498e","tid":983475,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T04:02:05.000Z","msg":"死左啦喎"}]}